# Walkthrough: Storyboard Conversion

I have converted your "Two Geese in Colombia" Walkthrough into a more accessible HTML format. This allows you to view the images and play the final animation directly in your web browser.

## Accomplishments

### Walkthrough Viewable as a Webpage
- Created [walkthrough.html](file:///Users/orestis/.gemini/antigravity/brain/e3c6a0c0-8ddd-4d01-8173-3ccbadf43318/walkthrough.html).
- Added premium CSS styling for a cleaner look.
- Embedded all original media (images and video) from the previous session.

## How to View as a Webpage
Simply copy the absolute path below and paste it into your browser's address bar:
`file:///Users/orestis/.gemini/antigravity/brain/e3c6a0c0-8ddd-4d01-8173-3ccbadf43318/walkthrough.html`

## How to Export as PDF
To save this walkthrough as a PDF:
1. Open the [walkthrough.html](file:///Users/orestis/.gemini/antigravity/brain/e3c6a0c0-8ddd-4d01-8173-3ccbadf43318/walkthrough.html) in your browser (Chrome or Safari).
2. Use the **Print** command (`Cmd + P`).
3. Set the **Destination** or **Printer** to **"Save as PDF"**.
4. Click **Save**.

> [!NOTE]
> Since PDFs are static documents, the video animation won't play inside the PDF, but all the high-resolution images and text will be preserved.
